// Semantic direction:
// cache_oblivious algorithms are optimal for all cache levels without knowing cache parameters.
// co_ideell_cache_modell assumes a two-level memory with unknown block size B and cache size M.
// co_tall_overføringer is the performance metric — minimize disk/cache block transfers.
// van_emde_boas_layout stores a static binary tree so any subtree of height h fits in O(2^h) blocks.
// veb_topphalvdel is the top ⌈h/2⌉ levels; veb_bunnhalvdel are the bottom ⌊h/2⌋ subtrees.
// funnel_sort achieves the optimal O((n/B) log_M n) cache transfers for comparison sorting.
// funnel_k is a k-way merge funnel: a complete binary tree of k² buffers.
// lazy_funnel_sort fills funnels lazily to reduce cache pressure at the lowest levels.
// co_matmul_rekursiv divides each matrix into four quadrants and recurses — 8 recursive calls.
// co_matmul_basistilfelle fires when a sub-matrix fits entirely in cache.
// co_statisk_tre stores a sorted array in VEB order for optimal search locality.
// prefetch_avstand_co is the number of iterations ahead to prefetch; typically 8–16 cache lines.
// non_temporal_store bypasses the cache for write-once streaming data.
// numa_lokal_allokering allocates memory on the NUMA node closest to the running thread.
// first_touch_policy is the default Linux policy: memory is allocated on the node that first writes it.
// transparent_hugepages automatically promotes 4KB pages to 2MB to reduce TLB pressure.
// false_sharing_unngåelse pads objects to cache_linje_størrelse so independent variables don't share lines.
// reuse_avstand is the number of distinct memory accesses between two accesses to the same location.

// Primitive flow:
// VEB layout bygg: rekursivt: top_halvdel -> bunnhalvdeler
//   inorder lagring: top-halvdel noder, deretter hvert bunnhalvdel-deltre
//   høyde h tre -> O(2^h/B) blokker for søk i noe nivå
// funnel_sort: bygg k-funnel med k² buffere i tre-form
//   fyll laveste buffer-nivå fra input -> flett opp
//   cache-effektivt: hvert nivå har buffere som passer i neste cache-nivå
// co_matmul: A(n×n) * B(n×n) = C(n×n)
//   del alle tre i 4 kvadranter: A00, A01, A10, A11 osv.
//   8 rekursive kall: C00 += A00*B00, C00 += A01*B10, ...
//   ved n ≈ √B: alle tre submatriser passer i cache -> ingen mer overføringer
// numa: allokér arbeidsdata nær trådens CPU
//   numa_bindning(tråd, node_0) -> malloc bruker node_0-minne
//   reduserer NUMA-fjernaksesser ~40%

// This defines cache-oblivious algorithms: ideal cache model, van Emde Boas layout, funnel
// sort, recursive matrix multiplication, VEB search trees, NUMA-aware allocation, TLB
// optimization with huge pages, false sharing avoidance, and memory access pattern analysis.
